high_descs: turn left, go to green counter top with red rags
pick up red rag in front
go to square sink to the left
place red rag in square sink, fill sink with water, pick up red rag from sink
turn left, go to right side of toilet
place red rag on right side of toilet tank
anns.task_desc: place cleaned red rag on right side of toilet tank

high_descs: Walk forward to the toilet, then turn left and walk to the red cloths on the counter.
Pick up the red cloth in the front from the counter.
Turn left and walk to the sink.
Put the cloth in the sink, rinse it off and take it out of the sink.
Turn around and walk to the toilet.
Put the cloth on the top of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned red cloth on the top of a toilet.

high_descs: Walk forward and turn left at the bath tub.
Pick up the wash cloth closest to you.
Move to your left to stand in front of the sink.
Rinse the cloth in the sink.
Turn around and go to the toilet.
Put the cloth on the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put a rinsed cloth on the toilet.
